addr: 2364 Adam Clayton Powell Blvd New York, NY
title: Dance Party With MsArtistry & Chry Baby
desc:
Multi Artistry Ent and La Femme Suite partners up to help support local New York rap artist Jaquae. Well known dancer and choregrapher Chry Baby Cozie and Dance Teacher MsArtistry teams up to help support Take Care of Harlem. 50% of the proceeds will go to a non-profit organization called Take Care Of Harlem, All guests will have a meet and greet with the artist after learning the dance moves. Come dance, network, party and give back.? 
 To Book An Music Artist With A Popular Dance Song Email: MultiArtistryEnt@gmail.com? 
 Avery Watson hopes to bring back that original Harlem dance culture by providing a platform for musicians and dancers to unite.
